+### !next
+Returns the name (string) of the next item in your deep‑research backlog/queue.
+
+**Usage**
+```shell
+!next [--queue <queue_name>]
+```
+If `--queue` is omitted, the default queue (`primary`) is used.
+
+**Returns**
+Plain‑text subject title, or `NONE` (case‑insensitive) if the queue is empty.
+
+**Example**
+```shell
+!next --queue cannabis_biology
+# → Soil-borne pathogen resistance in single‑plant grows
